lines.text: na cervenem vine a korenove zelenine, mackany
s omackou ze zeleneho pepre, steakove hranolky
s hribkovou omackou a restovanymi hribky,
s karamelizovanou cibulkou a bylinkovym maslem,
nase domaci houska, hovezi mlete, cheddar,
nalozene v nasi marinade, kozi rohy, okurek,
kureci maso, krutony, ancovickovy dresing a
nase bulka, dvojita porce naseho halloumi,
pizza corpus, jogurtovy dresing, ledovy salat,
cerne olivy, prosciutto crudo, rukola, balsamico
drcena rajcata, mozzarella, kureci maso, paprika,
drcena rajcata, mozzarella, cibule, paprika, cerne
